Not a big update in terms of the art, but a big update in terms of plot!

>In this world, female anthros exist as a direct result of divine punishment.
>There are no male anthros; God only punishes women.
>Certain men (and some lesbian/bi women) have developed romantic and sexual preferences for these furry women.
>Female protag (name: Victoria Kim) breaks up with her boyfriend when he confesses that he finds furry women the most attractive, for yet-undisclosed reasons.
>For a yet-undisclosed reason she decides to stalk her ex to a HMOFA meet-up and harasses everyone there.

I much prefer this story over the simpler premise I had originally of a girl upset that her boyfriend was a closet furry.

It'll be a bit of a slow burn, but there WILL be hmofa. As I'm using this project to improve as an artist, many of the poses and anatomy will be challenging, and so updates may be a bit slow; but hopefully the fact that it's a bunch of refined loose sketches will speed the process a bit.

One more important thing:
>Her vagina did not turn into a cookie, but it did turn black.

That's it for now! I'm very excited to share this story with everyone, and I hope the deeper plot sparks some new interest.
